---
---

<section id="about" class="py-32 px-6 relative">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <span class="section-num">01</span>

    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="font-mono text-sm tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 gradient-text">ABOUT</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-12">
        A bit about <span class="gradient-text">me</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Mobile profile photo -->
      <div class="reveal md:hidden flex justify-center mb-8">
        <div class="profile-glow">
          <img
            src="/profile.png"
            alt="Kaushik Kaja"
            class="w-48 h-48 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-white/10"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal space-y-6">
        <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          I'm a civil engineering student at UC Irvine with a minor in computer science,
          and I build at the intersection of hardware and software. From leading a
          world-champion FTC robotics team to interning at NASA and Kiewit, I've always
          been drawn to solving complex problems across disciplines.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Today I'm focused on AI-powered tools — building everything from browser agents
          that automate real-world tasks to 3D robot navigation systems and computational
          fact-checkers for drug discovery research.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl glass glow-hover">
            <p class="text-3xl font-black gradient-text mb-1">3.72</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/35">GPA at UCI</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl glass glow-hover">
            <p class="text-3xl font-black gradient-text mb-1">8+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/35">Projects Shipped</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl glass glow-hover">
            <p class="text-3xl font-black gradient-text mb-1">#1</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/35">FTC World Champion</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl glass glow-hover">
            <p class="text-3xl font-black gradient-text mb-1">NASA</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/35">Data Science Intern</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-32"></div>
</section>
